Package: elsa
Type: Package
Title: Entropy-based Local indicator of Spatial Association
Version: 0.0-2
Date: 2015-08-19
Author: Babak Naimi
Depends: methods, sp (>= 1.0-13), raster
Suggests: rgdal (>= 0.6-28)
Maintainer: Babak Naimi <naimi.b@gmail.com>
Description: A framework that provides the methods for quantifying local indicator of spatial association (ELSA), can be used for both continuous and categorical data. Moreover, global spatial structure can be measured using a variogram-like diagram, called entrogram.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: http://r-gis.net